{"tid":2236473,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"檢測公司到蘭桂坊派樣本樽　下周一派員收集","createTime":"2020-10-09T13:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T14:15:59.000Z","uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4f3c02014020c4eed98a7d2a6428c304fb19c942","tid":2236473,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:09:41.000Z","msg":"當局透過檢測公司到蘭桂坊，以流動車輛向酒吧職員和顧客，派發深喉唾液樣本樽。<br />\n<br />\n檢測公司負責人楊先生表示，流動車輛會由傍晚6時至午夜停留在中環雲咸街，他們準備了1000個深喉唾液樣本樽，會有職員直接派發給酒吧職員和市民，市民亦可親自到流動車輛上領取。<br />\n<br />\n檢測公司下周一會派員到酒吧收集樣本樽，市民並可將樣本樽交到位於鰂魚涌海澤街的流動收集車。<br />\n<br />\n檢測公司分別會在周六及周日，到尖沙咀諾士佛台和灣仔駱克道派發樣本樽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553880-20201009.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553880-20201009.htm&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzobCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=2bd63ed0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553880-20201009.htm&h=fe761b3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553880-20201009.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a2b2aad6c72b709f79cc9441bb035627cd59a3b9","tid":2236473,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />深喉會做既, 不過唔係你呢D囉"},{"pid":"41c488c9c8e2d1e180fa6a0b6a7488c2384e70c9","tid":2236473,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"上次呢間野篤數，明明無做都話你有做過，仲全部陰性"},{"pid":"751bacfbc1d87860365b6e4ddb33bc97978023c1","tid":2236473,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZCkNPm5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCkNPm5.png&h=d9b317e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"482fd87c332489b5884beb0adfac96b12ae55d99","tid":2236473,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,